'''Rabad''' was a [[Communications officer/Legends|communications officer]] serving in the [[Galactic Alliance Defense Fleet]]. He was stationed onboard the [[Admiral Ackbar (Victory-class)|''Admiral Ackbar'']], and was [[Death/Legends|killed]] by [[Gorog]] [[Assassin/Legends|assassins]] in [[36 ABY]].

